title: OCE streamers looking for support
body:
Hey guys i've recently started up a stream at https://www.twitch.tv/azrael62551 . I'm a D5 jg main so tune in if you find the time.

More so what i'm interested in is if anyone who is an OCE streamer could post their streams as well so that we can help grow the OCE streamer community by showing each other support.

P.S didn't know what board to post this in so i just went miscellaneous.

replies.body: I thought I recognised that name haha. I shall check out your streams next time you're on good luck dude!

You'd post it in the *Player Creations* category, and you wouldn't be allowed to promote your stream more than once a week.

I hope this helps with the "P.S."

As for other OCE streamers, since I'm guessing you know of Midbeast, the are *Panda Annie* (#1 Annie OCE, #2 world) and *Zoencidence* (#1 Zoe World).

{{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}

Thankyou very much for taking the time to reply :)

I'll remember in future to post in that category.
I would stream, but my net is god awful, and i already lag as is...
